v creation,\nimported entries from oleans, and locally added entries). `localEntries` tracks entries\nadded in the current module so they can be exported into the olean.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Linter/Init.html#Lean.Linter.LinterSetsState","kind":"structure","line":32,"name":"Lean.Linter.LinterSetsState","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Linter/Init.lean#L32-L41"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Linter/Init.html#Lean.Linter.insertLinterSetEntry\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Linter</span>.<span class=\"name\">insertLinterSetEntry</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">map</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Linter/Init.html#Lean.Linter.LinterSets\">LinterSets</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">setName</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">options</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Data/NameMap/Basic.html#Lean.NameSet\">NameSet</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Linter/Init.html#Lean.Linter.LinterSets\">LinterSets</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Insert a set into a `LinterSets` map.\n\n`entry.1` is the name of the linter set,\n`entry.2` contains the names of the set's linter options.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Linter/Init.html#Lean.Linter.insertLinterSetEntry","kind":"def","line":23,"name":"Lean.Linter.insertLinterSetEntry","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Linter/Init.lean#L23-L30"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Linter/Init.html#Lean.Linter.instI